- [What is Topic Modeling?](https://www.analyticsvidhya.com/blog/2016/08/beginners-guide-to-topic-modeling-in-python/)

**TL;DR** :

Topic modeling is a technique in natural language processing (NLP) that aims to uncover hidden thematic structures within a collection of text documents. It helps identify and organize the main topics or themes present in a large set of text data.
